        <ExplanationTxt>THE CYPRESS OF RALEIGH CLUB WAS FORMED TO SERVE AS THE MANAGEMENT ENTITY WHICH CARRIES OUT THE CONTRACTUAL AGREEMENT WITH MEMBERS OF THE CONTINUING CARE RETIREMENT COMMUNITY. THE CLUB MANAGES THE COMMONLY OWNED PROPERTY OF THE CYPRESS, INCLUDING THE CLUBHOUSE AND HEALTH CENTER, AS WELL AS THE SERVICES PROVIDED AT THE CLUBHOUSE AND HEALTH CENTER.</ExplanationTxt>
