        <ExplanationTxt>MANAGEMENT MONITORS TRANSACTIONS AND ACTIVITIES CLOSELY. THE MANAGEMENT COMPANY PROVIDES OVERSIGHT IN DAILY ACTIVITES AND TRANSACTIONS.</ExplanationTxt>
